reviewText: Disappointed about his acting. Not funny.
This was just what i was looking for. Brought back childhood memories. The quality of the dvd was excellent. Didnt take long to ship and im vey happy with it.

Tin Tan es tan comico como los hermanos don Ramon y el loco Valdez. la pelicula la consegui para un miembro de la familia, ya van varias veces q la vemos desde q la compre, es una pelicula de familia.
